casebody.data:
Stephanie HARRIS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Roman Valerievich GOLOVIN and Viktoriia Golovina, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1940 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 26, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SUAREZ and SALTER, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 31, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
